{"data":[{"id":563796526,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bdca297125f927cc1ecd4e3d61f2ca16","url_token":"xiaoyu-88-71","name":"xiaoyu","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bdca297125f927cc1ecd4e3d61f2ca16","user_type":"people","headline":"cs undergraduate","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563796526","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2dca39e75c97365379d350731fe851db_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546278503,"updated_time":1546278503,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":5,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e大家不要纠结他所说的-1是负质数，实际上我认为他的意思是新创立一个叫“质数”的集合，他如果这样表示的话还有看下去的欲望，我们不妨把他的思路改成这样：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e设有一个集合P',P’=P∪{-1}，P是质数集合，这样P'就是他口中所谓的质数（包含他所谓的正质数和唯一的负质数-1）集合（先不要管实际不存在），我们先按着这个思路走，然后指出他证明中一个比较明显的错误来证明他的证明是错的：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 他图片中的第六行自己定义的命题：若-1是质数，该质数就是所谓的P集合.......   然后怎么怎么样\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后他图中第十二行原命题是真命题，即若-1是质数（P），2n∈A，（A是他说的为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数）  那么他推出他的哥猜变式一是对的，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e错就错在这个逻辑，因为此时他的哥猜变式后半部分为2n=-1+(2n-1)  而2n-1并不是质数，更谈不上是集合A了，所以他企图通过证明后半部分恒成立故哥猜变式正确，然后接下来证明2n∈B恒成立就不成立了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e附下原证明和原图\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4fc62fbedfc1583fa395ac15cc01ba56_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-raww